OL,6,F"Even kicking things. And, whilst I
OL,7,Fnever considered that to be physical
OL,8,Fabuse, in actual fact it is because
OL,9,Fit's the intimation that if you don't
OL,10,Fdo what I'm saying, you're going to be
OL,11,Fnext."
OL,13,FJack - not his real name - has been
OL,14,Fmarried to wife Sarah for 15 years.
OL,16,FTheir relationship hit crisis point
OL,17,Fthree years ago when Sarah, whose real
OL,18,Fidentity we are also protecting,
OL,19,Ffinally recognised his behaviour as
OL,20,Fabusive.
