OL,6,F"He used to sort of belittle me and
OL,7,Fsay that I was useless at most things
OL,8,Fin the house," she says.
OL,10,F"So it got to the point where I didn't
OL,11,Fwant to do anything in the house
OL,12,Fbecause I was frightened (about what
OL,13,Fwould happen) if I didn't do it his
OL,14,Fway. Because it had to be his way - or
OL,15,Fhe lost his temper.
