OL,6,F"It wasn't until I went for
OL,7,Fcounselling for something else -
OL,8,Fbereavement - that I opened up about
OL,9,Fcertain things my husband did and she
OL,10,Fsaid 'I'm not saying you're in an
OL,11,Fabusive relationship, but'. And then
OL,12,Fas soon as she said that I thought,
OL,13,Fyes I am."
OL,15,F'Society has got a certain image of a
OL,16,Fman'
OL,18,FSarah told Jack if he didn't seek help
OL,19,Ffor his behaviour she was going to
OL,20,Fleave.
