OL,6,FHe signed up for the Inspire to Change
OL,7,Fprogramme, led by the charity
OL,8,FCranstoun - a six-month scheme to help
OL,9,Fabusers change their behaviour.
OL,11,FJack says: "They're just so simple -
OL,12,Fsome of the things they teach and show
OL,13,Fyou - but they're things I think many
OL,14,Fmen would just miss in their normal
OL,15,Feveryday life."
OL,17,FHe says there is "no real reason" why
OL,18,Fhe didn't recognise his own behaviour
OL,19,Fbefore joining the programme.
