OL,3,CThe men taking part in group sessions
OL,4,Cfor self-confessed domestic abusers
OL,6,F"All I can say is society has got a
OL,7,Fcertain image of a man and this is
OL,8,Fhanded down generation after
OL,9,Fgeneration and we have got to look at
OL,10,Fhow as a society generally we teach
OL,11,Fyoung men," he said.
OL,13,FCranstoun uses one-to-one and group
OL,14,Fsessions to help participants
OL,15,Frecognise the signs of abuse,
OL,16,Funderstand why they use violence or
OL,17,Faggression in relationships, and
OL,18,Fdevelop practical tools to change.
