OL,6,FThe Inspire to Change Programme in
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire has helped more than
OL,8,F200 men since 2021, but is one of a
OL,9,Fdwindling number of perpetrator
OL,10,Fintervention schemes.
OL,12,FWayne Grocott, service manager, said:
OL,13,F"Historically a lot of domestic abuse
OL,14,Fservices have been around victim
OL,15,Fsurvivor support - as they should, and
OL,16,FI can't stress that enough.
