OL,6,FA recent report found just 7% of
OL,7,Fsurvivors who wanted their abuser to
OL,8,Freceive support were able to access
OL,9,Fit, with local authority funding for
OL,10,Finitiatives like this and other
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse services fluctuating
OL,12,Facross Yorkshire and Lincolnshire.
OL,14,FIn Calderdale, for example, the amount
OL,15,Fspent on such services rose 52% from
OL,16,F2022 to 2024. In Linconlshire it
OL,17,Fincreased by 37%. But North
OL,18,FYorkshire's budget remained the same.
OL,19,FAnd in Kirklees the budget was cut by
OL,20,F24%.
