OL,6,FYorkshire's largest domestic abuse
OL,7,Fcharity IDAS said demand for its
OL,8,Fservices has doubled in the last four
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FCommunity team manager Erica Marsland
OL,12,Fsaid: "We're in a position that some
OL,13,Fadditional funding that's been given
OL,14,Fthroughout the sector is due to end in
OL,15,FMarch 2025.
OL,17,F"The impact of that is absolutely
OL,18,Fmassive.
