OL,6,F"We might have to look at reducing our
OL,7,Fstaffing which will impact the support
OL,8,Fwe can provide which will be
OL,9,Fdetrimental to the safety of our
OL,10,Fsurvivors."
OL,12,FFellow charity worker Noreen Akhtar
OL,13,Fadded: "We're hoping we'll get an
OL,14,Fextension on that funding, but at this
OL,15,Fmoment we're at that crossroads where
OL,16,Fwe don't know what the future looks
