OL,6,FCriminologist Dr Sam Lewis leads a
OL,7,Fteam at the University of Leeds which
OL,8,Fresearches violence against women and
OL,9,Fgirls.
OL,11,FShe said the rise in women seeking
OL,12,Fsupport was partly down to growing
OL,13,Fawareness, but also an increase in
OL,14,Fmisogyny.
OL,16,F"I think there is a great deal more
OL,17,Fawareness which is fantastic and the
OL,18,Fmore we talk about it the more people
OL,19,Fwill be able to report their
OL,20,Fexperiences", she said.
