OL,6,F"But often if we go back far enough
OL,7,Fpeople didn't have ways of meeting
OL,8,Fother people with similar misogynistic
OL,9,Fattitudes now online you can meet
OL,10,Fpeople who share perhaps your very
OL,11,Fnegative interests or beliefs.
OL,13,F"So I think the online environment has
OL,14,Fcreated a very dangerous space and
OL,15,Fthose kinds of environments leak out
OL,16,Finto broader society."
